items.title: Vectoring
items.description: With my creative mindset and artistic talent, I create sleek, scalable icons, logos, and illustrations that add a special touch to any product.

items.title: Web Design
items.description: Utilizing my artistry, UX skills, and background in web development, I create a clean UI that speaks to the user.

items.title: Testing
items.description: As a former QA Engineer, I test my own designs and challenge workflows to see how they can be improved upon.

items.title: Empathy
items.description: I put the user at the forefront of my design decisions and understand the value of user personas.

items.title: Research
items.description: I strive to gain a deeper grasp of the subject matter and competing products, and gather feedback from potential users.

items.title: Teamwork
items.description: My team is very important to me, and I strive to understand their roles and provide support wherever I can.
